snippet.title: Amber Heard and Elon Musk's Private Texts EXPOSED
snippet.description:
Amber Heard texted SpaceX founder, Elon Musk several days before she filed for divorce from Johnny Depp and clearly Elon Musk wants to be more than friends with Amber. Elon Musk has texted Amber, ‘ I really like you’. A transcript of the text messages has been brought to public by Johnny Depp’s lawyer, Adam Waldman.
Proposing to “arrange 24/7 security” for the actress, the billionaire wrote, “the offer would stand, even if you never wanted to see me again.”
